The panel was comprised of 10 people many of whom were involved in local government and local law enforcement from Robertson and Sumner Counties.
Portland Mayor Mike Callis moderated the evenings discussion.
There are very few families that have not been touched by this if its not overdose death its a child that youve seen absolutely just be torn from you because their entire personality has been stolen by the love of the drug State Representative and event panelist William Lamberth said.
