Narcotics detectives say the two provided Aylward with the Fentanyl a prescription opioid typically used to manage severe pain.
As detectives continued to work on this case they identified Michael Lacefield 28 and Ellis 19 as the persons who originally sold and delivered the Fentanyl-laced heroin to the apartment according to police.
