Because Ellis was 17 years old when Aylward died police have charged him in juvenile court.
The second degree murder charges against Wise Thompson and Lacefield are pending in Davidson County criminal court police say. They're scheduled to appear in court Dec. 15.
Indicted in the same case on felony heroin charges is James Cooke 39 who police said shipped the Fentanyl-laced heroin from Detroit to Nashville.
